{"type": "article", "id": 15987, "title": "“Autumn Night”", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-13T06:10:28Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 90, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135112aJy50sBj2mTFDWOh.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tAlexander McQueen 旗下的 Puma 和日本球鞋品牌 atmos 联合推出了 Disc Blaze 鞋型的新款“Autumn Night”。在深蓝色的鞋身上点缀着亮点，营造出繁星满天或在城市中亮起斑斓灯光的景象。鞋底更使用天蓝色的夜光材质，让这款鞋成为黑暗中亮点。<a href=\"http://www.atmos-tokyo.com/category/ATMOS/360497_01.html\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143424I1cvghHMlUt62P9m.jpg\" width=\"780\" height=\"520\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261434240KJhMywT6UZaOuCl.jpg\" width=\"545\" height=\"499\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.91559633\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143425GXHJwbiaYIRTvgfP.jpg\" width=\"535\" height=\"529\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.98878505\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143425LtKOPiIBASMcuXwk.jpg\" width=\"567\" height=\"343\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.60493827\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}